msgid "document"
msgstr ""

#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:26
#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:103
msgid ""
"The index specification document to use as the :doc:`shard key </core"
"/sharding-shard-key/>`. The shard key determines how MongoDB distributes "
"the documents among the shards."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:30
#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:107
msgid ""
"The *key* of the index specification document is the field to use as the "
"shard key. The *value* of the document must be one of the following:"
msgstr ""

#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:34
#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:111
msgid "``1`` to indicate forward traversal for the field."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:36
#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:113
msgid "``-1`` to indicate reverse traversal for the field."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:38
#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:115
msgid "``\"hashed\"`` to specify a :ref:`hashed shard key <hashed-shard-keys>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:41
#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:118
msgid ""
"Unless the collection is empty, the index must exist prior to the "
":dbcommand:`shardCollection` command. If the collection is empty, MongoDB"
" creates the index prior to sharding the collection if the index that can"
" support the shard key does not already exist."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:46
#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:123
msgid "See also :ref:`sharding-shard-key-indexes`"
msgstr ""

#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:50
msgid "``unique``"
msgstr ""

#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:52
msgid "boolean"
msgstr ""

#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:54
#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:129
msgid ""
"When ``true``, the ``unique`` option ensures that the underlying index "
"enforces a unique constraint. Hashed shard keys do not support unique "
"constraints. Defaults to ``false``."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:60
msgid "``numInitialChunks``"
msgstr ""

#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:62
msgid "integer"
msgstr ""

#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:64
#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:137
msgid ""
"Specifies the number of chunks to create initially when sharding an "
"*empty* collection with a :ref:`hashed shard key <sharding-hashed-"
"sharding>`. MongoDB will then create and balance chunks across the "
"cluster. The ``numInitialChunks`` must be less than ``8192`` per shard."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:72
#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:145
msgid ""
"If the collection is not empty or the shard key is not a hashed key, the "
"operation returns an error."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:77
msgid "``collation``"
msgstr ""

#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:81
#: ../source/includes/apiargs/dbcommand-shardCollection-field.rst:152
msgid ""
"Optional. If the collection specified to ``shardCollection`` has a "
"default :doc:`collation </reference/collation>`, you *must* include a "
"collation document with ``{ locale : \"simple\" }``, or the "
"``shardCollection`` command fails. At least one of the indexes whose "
"fields support the shard key pattern must have the simple collation."
msgstr ""

